markets.rules_primary: If the highest temperature recorded in Central Park, New York for February 08, 2026 as reported by the National Weather Service's Climatological Report (Daily), is less than 17°, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Not all weather data is the same. Preliminary NWS reporting and measurement methods may be subject to underlying rounding and conversion nuances. Traders should exercise caution when interpreting preliminary NWS data.
